description:
A single-edged, warped sword forged by a master craftsman in the eastern Japan
Its name is "Kotetsu". [Range 1]
name: Kotetsu

description:
A ninja sword that hides its wielder from the eyes of the opponent.
Its name is "Hagakure".[Range 1] [Evasion +10%]
name: Hagakure

description:
A ninja's straight sword with a beautiful flame-like blade pattern.
Its name is "Homura". [Range 1] [Critical rate +10%]
name: Homura

description:
A beautiful jet-black sword.
Its name is "Jorogumo". [Range 1] [Poison +20%]
name: Jorōgumo

description:
A short sword with a design of a three-legged crow.
Its name is "Yatagarasu". [Range 1], [Movement +1].
name: Yatagarasu

description:
A divine sword with a will that grows with its wielder. Its name is "Hyakkimaru".
[Range 1] [The higher the level, the more powerful] [Learning: Hyakki Yakou]
name: Hyakkimaru

description:
己の肉体を武器とする者が使う武器。守りに向く。
【射程 1】
name: Copper Gauntlet

description:
A large gauntlet that prioritizes defense over counterattacking.
[Range 1] [Response change: Defense: Damage reduction]
name: Guardian Gauntlet

description:
A gauntlet imbued with a spell that reflects the opponent's magic.
[Range 1] [Response Change: Magic Reflection: Reflects opponent's magic]
name: Magic Mirror Gauntlet

description:
A gauntlet of an armed priest who returns healing miracles when receiving support from allies.
[Range 1] [Response change: Blessing: Opponent's HP recovery/Range 3]
name: Blessed Gauntlet

description:
A Roman weapon of an armed priest whose fists fly with the miracle of the gods.
[Range 5 (straight/line of sight)]
name: Rocket Punch

description:
A long spear used by many. Its strength is its long range.
[Range 2]
name: Long Spear

description:
A heavy spear originally used on horseback. Hard to handle,
but powerful. [Range 3 (Straight)]
name: Assault Lance

description:
A long spear used to attack the center of the enemy army
from the side line. [Range 4 (diagonal)]
name: Cross Pike

description:
A throwing spear made for the purpose of throwing. It is suitable for the rear guard.
[Range 2-3]
name: Javelin

description:
A beautifully decorated white silver spear. It transforms the wielder's life into power.
[Range 2] [Holy] [Power increases with remaining HP]
name: Holy Spear Angela

description:
A jet-black spear with hideous decorations. It turns the owner's danger into power.
[Range 2] [Darkness] [Power increases as remaining HP decreases]
name: Curse Spear Diablo

description:
A small, easy-to-carry bow favored by scouts and assassins.
[Range 2-4]
name: Smart Bow

description:
A small bow for hunting. It is more powerful when handled by moving around.
[Range 1-3] [The more distance you move, the more powerful it becomes.
name: Hunting Bow

description:
A large bow made for combat. It is more powerful to handle on the spot.
[Range 3-5] [Power increases as movement decreases]
name: Dragon Roar

description:
A magic bow imbued with division magic. Can attack up to 3 target at once.
[Range 2-4] [Area Range 3] [Can attack up to 3 targets]
name: Comet Star

description:
A ritual bow decorated with gold. The farther away you attack, the stronger it becomes.
[Range 2-6] [Power increases as distance to opponent increases]
name: Shining Bow "Valkyrie"

description:
A huge battle axe made of steel. A weapon that can only be handled by those with strength.
[Range 1]
name: Battle Ax

description:
Throwing axe with heavy blade. Can be used
for long-range attacks. [Range 3]
name: Francesca

description:
A battle axe with earth magic applied. It can attack
the surrounding area. [Perimeter attack 1]
name: Ground Breaker

description:
A magnificent battle axe for heroes. It shows its true power when it is at full strength.
[Range 1] [Power is greatly increased only when HP is full]
name: Heroic Saga

description:
A battle axe for those who have mastered the art of fighting. The more you fight, the stronger it becomes.
[Range 1] [The more TP you have, the more powerful it becomes.
name: Battle Master

description:
A grimoire containing fire magic. It is useful in cold weather.
[Cannot counterattack] [Learned: Elfire, Flare Land]
name: Red Flame Grimoire

description:
A grimoire containing ice magic. Everyone equips it in summer.
[Cannot counterattack] [Learned: Ice Sword, Frozen]
name: White Ice Grimoire

description:
A grimoire containing lightning magic. The tingling is addictive.
[Cannot fight] [Learned: Thunderbolt, Lightning]
name: Purple Lightning Grimoire

description:
A grimoire containing absorption magic. Children should not look at it.
[Cannot counterattack] [Learned: Life Divide, Magic Snatch]
name: Vampire Grimoire

description:
A grimoire containing light magic. A glowing book that can be used as a substitute for a light.
[Cannot counterattack] [Learned: Holy Arrow, Shine]
name: Luminosity Grimoire

description:
A grimoire containing forbidden dark magic. Maniacal contents.
[Cannot counterattack] [Learned: Darkness, Chaos Gate]
name: Abyssal Grimoire

description:
A self-defense dagger favored by travelers. It does not fight strightly.
[Range 2 (diagonal)
name: Traveler's Dagger

description:
A dagger wielded in place of a shield. Concentrate on parrying attacks.
[Range 2 (diagonal)] [Response change: Dodge: Physical evasion 25%]
name: Left Hand Dagger

description:
A dagger that uses magic to create a blade. Used by magicians and priests for self-defense.
[Range 2 (diagonal)] [Magical attack].
name: Magic Dagger

description:
A dagger infused with wind magic. The more you blow through, the stronger it becomes.
[Range 2 (diagonal)] [Power increases as movement increases]
name: Gale Dagger

description:
A dagger for dancers that can be wielded as if dancing.
[Perimeter attack 2-4]
name: Dancer's Dagger

description:
A weapon that uses magical power as a bullet. Unlike a bow, the line of fire is blocked by enemies.
[Learning: Ether Buster]
name: Ether Buster

description:
A magic gun that fires bullets with spells that match the opponent's level.
[Learning: Level 5 Death]
name: Level 5 Death

description:
A magic gun made to fight enemies stronger than you.
[Learning: Giant Killing]
name: Giant Killing

description:
A magic gun that uses its own vitality as a bullet. The first digit is important.
[Learning: 1st Digit Sniper]
name: 1st Digit Sniper

description:
A super bombardment by a magical weapon floating in the sky.
[Learn: Stellar Blaster].
name: Stellar Blaster

description:
A shining sword for the brave. The more you fight, the more powerful it becomes.
[Range 1] [The higher the opponent's level, the more powerful it becomes.
name: Brave Sword
